  - 775
By: Rûmî
---
The world of sense and colour ... is a narrow prison.

The cause of narrowness is composition (compoundness) and number
(plurality)： the senses are moving towards composition.

Know that the world of Unification lies beyond sense： if you want
Unity, march in that direction.
